{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c477d4cbd5","title":"有关“华侨政策”的言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52843e3e89","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c477d4cbd5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d0fe9c9b0e","name":"厦门大学师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8baec577e3","type":"title","text":"有关“华侨政策”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"977441adba","type":"authors","text":"厦门大学师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"965a405559","type":"paragraph","text":"梁显华：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"ad3de4a44d","type":"paragraph","text":"“国家的侨务政策是用来侮辱华侨的，许多华侨都不满，国家对华侨的特殊照顾与台湾对华侨的欺骗一样，这是为了达到收买华侨的政治目的，那些侨委会的干部简直是违法乱纪”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"5739957299","type":"paragraph","text":"郑朝宗：“对华侨的政策是怀柔政策。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"639d42b85e","type":"paragraph","text":"历史系陈遂良：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"106dcfd3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"“土改将华侨土地分出去，华侨思想搞不通，万一侨汇断了，侨属又要卖故衣。”“要利用侨汇，但又对华侨很不关心，华侨都买不到米吃，照顾很少。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"97514c6e80","type":"paragraph","text":"“有钱人入门(指华侨回国)就有人捧候、请开会、宴客……，大捧而特捧；无钱的没有人过问，贫侨回国简直给泼了一桶冷水，工作无着一拖几年，生活无着忧也忧死。有钱的争取工作较容易，会捧、吹牛的也好；忠直的就没有，一点钱用完，生活就成问题。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"31b7ec85ce","type":"paragraph","text":"“侨务政策还是照顾富侨多，贫侨只是沾沾光，有的连加入侨联都没门可入，提代表性只是大肚(指富侨)。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"9b8b6c2254","type":"paragraph","text":"“侨联吸收会员，无钱的做散蜂，有钱的登记表送上门”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"e02465a8d0","type":"paragraph","text":"“华侨知识分子回国感慨很多，多谈吗政治问题、思想问题，给别人引起怀疑”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"},{"id":"53a6bd4024","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：中共厦门大学委员会宣传部编印《右派反动言论集》，1957年9月20日。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5"}],"page":{"id":"700abaeb6e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c477d4cbd5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}